title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 82-2.9 - Witnesses
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 §§ 82-2.9 - Witnesses

State Regulations

At the time set for the commencement of the hearing, the
parties will present to the chairperson of the panel copies of any subpoenas
served on prospective witnesses. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8
§§
82-2.9

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
